        <summary>What are the security risks of using unverified downloading tools?</summary>
        <p>Many third-party downloaders, especially free web-based ones, are fraught with security risks. They often bundle malware, execute aggressive intrusive advertising, or attempt to steal user credentials and personal data.</p>
      </details>
